# ==== Build directories (CMake/VS) ====
Build/
build/
**/Build/
**/build/
out/
cmake-build-*/

# ==== CMake generated files ====
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
CTestTestfile.cmake
install_manifest.txt
Testing/
**/CMakeScripts/
**/*Targets.cmake
**/*Config.cmake

# ==== Visual Studio / MSVC ====
.vs/
*.sln
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.*
*.vcproj*
*.vcxitems*
*.ipch
*.opendb
*.VC.db*
*.tlog
*.lastbuildstate
*.user
*.suo
x64/
x86/
Debug/
Release/
RelWithDebInfo/
MinSizeRel/

